{"type": "article", "id": 17483, "title": "带两边抽屉的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-13T06:10:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 87, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071224326WkObqQpMtJh4me1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是葡萄牙的工作室 Gonçalo Campos 最新发布的桌子，两边都有抽屉，可以供两个人相对而坐。掀开侧边的桌板也是一个放小东西的柜子，特别在于里面留有空隙的板，可以将电脑线或者手机充电线牵下去，是适应社会更新的设计。这家工作室还设计了不少有趣味的桌子，<a href=\"http://www.wewood.eu/products/desks/metis\" target=\"_blank\">这里是他们的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144602chXL2tkaNxMSPK5U.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"975\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.90277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144602hGsEm2zug8vCHLOl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"562\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.93666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144602qGC6OI1B34xwZPgh.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"520\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144603Dkax6VwLlWbuIojq.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.01333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}